    <h3>.plain</h3>
    <p>Removes the dotted underline while preserving the title tooltip. Use when the visual indicator is not needed.</p>
    <div class="example">
      <p>Use <abbr class="plain" title="Cascading Style Sheets">CSS</abbr> for styling web pages.</p>
    </div>
    <code-block language="html" label="Plain abbreviation without underline">{{ plainAbbrCode | safe }}</code-block>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Live Examples</h2>

    <h3>Technical Abbreviations</h3>
    <div class="example">
      <p>The <abbr title="Document Object Model">DOM</abbr> allows <abbr title="JavaScript">JS</abbr> to manipulate <abbr title="HyperText Markup Language">HTML</abbr> elements.</p>
    </div>

    <h3>Organization Names</h3>
    <div class="example">
      <p><abbr title="National Aeronautics and Space Administration">NASA</abbr> launched the <abbr title="James Webb Space Telescope">JWST</abbr> in 2021.</p>
    </div>

    <h3>With Definition</h3>
    <p>Combine with <code>&lt;dfn&gt;</code> when first defining a term.</p>
    <div class="example">
      <p><dfn><abbr title="Application Programming Interface">API</abbr></dfn> is a set of protocols for building software applications.</p>
    </div>
